ygData.subject: Where are Tinny daggers in Qeynos?
ygData.msgSnippet: Hy all, I have a little problem as i created erudite enchanter and after first 8 lv i crossed a ocean without many tinny daggers. WHERE i can find tinny
ygData.messageBody:
Hy all,

I have a little problem as i created erudite enchanter and after first 8 lv
i crossed a ocean without many tinny daggers.
WHERE i can find tinny daggers in qeynos? i dont wish to travel back to
erudin or to freeport as some enchanters suggested when i asked them in
game. I cannot belive that is possible that in qeynos dont exist seller of
tinny dagers, it is so big city there must be one seller but maybe hard to
find i spent nearly a day searching but i dont find it. Please if you know
where it is to share it with this list so that a enchanters dont have to
travel to other side of ocean or to freeport to get daggers.

Thanks in advance

Dilith 8 lv Enchanter, Soulsek Ro
